  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0da2\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0d9a \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0db8 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd4\u0db4\u0da7\u0dad\u0dca \u0dad\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4  \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0daf\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "They are also trying to tap the government employee pension",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Ranjith Maddumabandara, appointed member of Samagi Janabalawega, said in Parliament that they are trying to tap the pension of government employees by adopting a contributory pension system.",
        "Mr. Maddumabandara said that pension is the right of public servants and now they are trying to work on it too.",
        "Joining the debate on the last day of the budget, Mr. Maddumabandara said that the former Prime Minister and his colleagues are giving advice to the President today."
      ],
